imdb.plot outline: The unrelated and pseudonymous Andy Warski and Chris Warski discuss everything from politics and social issues to YouTube drama and lucid dreaming on their live comedy podcast featuring a variety of often-controversial guests. Later, as the format changes to internet bloodsports (a no-insults-barred form of debating), Andy finds a new co-host in the silver-tongued Jean-François Gariépy, but their disparate personalities soon clash.
imdb.title: Warski Live
plot: 'Andy Warski' (qv) and his co-host (first 'Chris Warski' (qv), then 'Jean-François Gariépy' (qv), then 'Jay Dyer' (qv)) discuss a wide range of topics on their live comedy podcast featuring a variety of often-controversial guests.::J. Spurlin
